{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-299","title":"男女平等","sectionId":"chapter-13","sectionTitle":"舆论焦点要关注","pageStart":1452,"pageEnd":1456,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":12,"duplicateEntryCount":18,"pages":[{"number":1452,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"299 男女平等"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"}]},{"number":1453,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"fair play 公平竞争","headword":"fair play"},{"type":"entry","text":"equal opportunity 机会均等","headword":"equal opportunity"},{"type":"entry","text":"participate equally 平等参与","headword":"participate equally"},{"type":"entry","text":"right to vote 选举权","headword":"right to vote"},{"type":"entry","text":"equality in employment 平等就业","headword":"equality in employment"},{"type":"entry","text":"equal pay for equal work 同工同酬","headword":"equal pay for equal work"},{"type":"entry","text":"respect women 尊重女性","headword":"respect women"},{"type":"entry","text":"masculinity [ˌmæskjuˈlɪnəti]","headword":"masculinity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.阳刚之气"},{"type":"entry","text":"discriminate against women 歧视妇女","headword":"discriminate against women"}]},{"number":1454,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"blame for 因…而责备","headword":"blame for"},{"type":"entry","text":"critical consciousness批判意识","headword":"critical consciousness"},{"type":"entry","text":"feminine consciousness女性意识","headword":"feminine consciousness"}]},{"number":1455,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Gender discrimination is a hotly contested issue.（性别歧视是一"},{"type":"text","text":"个争论激烈的话题。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Do you have any thought on that?（这个问题你怎么看？）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：We should eliminate inequality.（我们应该消除不平等。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, men and women are equal.（是啊，男性和女性是平等"},{"type":"text","text":"的。）"}]},{"number":1456,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"Chapter1